---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="개발서비스 - RefX" description="AI/음성 기술 파이프라인, Spring Boot 백엔드, AWS 클라우드 인프라 및 DevOps 자동화 서비스를 제공합니다.">
  <Header />

  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-refx-primary to-blue-700 text-white py-20">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">AI 기술과 백엔드 개발의 전문가</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <strong>STT, TTS, LLM, Voice AI</strong> 파이프라인 구축 경험과<br>
            <strong>Claude Code AI 자동화 + MCP + AWS ECS Fargate, CodePipeline</strong> 기반 운영 자동화로<br>
            엔터프라이즈급 AI 솔루션을 제공합니다
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Services -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            실전 검증된 전문 서비스
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
            <strong>마고 프로젝트 AI 플랫폼</strong> 구축과 <strong>대기업 서비스 운영</strong> 경험을 바탕으로<br>
            AI 기술 파이프라인부터 클라우드 인프라 자동화까지 종합 솔루션을 제공합니다
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- AI/Voice Technology -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border-2 border-purple-200">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full mb-2">AI 특화</span>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">AI/Voice 기술 솔루션</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">음성 AI 파이프라인 및 플랫폼 구축</p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">STT/TTS 파이프라인</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">음성-텍스트 변환 및 텍스트-음성 합성 시스템</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">LLM 통합</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">대규모 언어 모델 연동 및 프롬프트 엔지니어링</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Vocal Biomarker</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">음성 기반 건강 지표 분석 기술</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Voice Emotion Recognition</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">음성 감정 인식 및 분석 시스템</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Backend Development -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-refx-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">백엔드 시스템 개발</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">고성능, 확장 가능한 서버 애플리케이션 구축</p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-refx-primary rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Spring Boot 4.x.x (최신)</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">최신 Spring 생태계를 활용한 엔터프라이즈급 애플리케이션</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-refx-primary rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Java 25 LTS</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">2025년 9월 출시 LTS 버전, Virtual Threads 및 최신 기능 적용</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-refx-primary rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">WebFlux & 반응형 프로그래밍</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">논블로킹 I/O를 통한 높은 처리량 달성</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-refx-primary rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">API 설계 및 구현</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">RESTful API, GraphQL, 마이크로서비스 아키텍처</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Cloud Infrastructure -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">AWS 클라우드 인프라</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">확장 가능하고 안정적인 클라우드 아키텍처</p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">ECS Fargate</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">서버리스 컨테이너 오케스트레이션 및 자동 스케일링</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">CodePipeline & CodeBuild</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">AWS 네이티브 CI/CD 파이프라인 구축</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">RDS & ElastiCache</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">고가용성 데이터베이스 및 캐싱 레이어</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">ALB & Auto Scaling</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">로드밸런싱 및 탄력적 확장 구성</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- DevOps & Automation -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border-2 border-green-200">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full mb-2">운영 특화</span>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">DevOps & 운영 자동화</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">실서비스 운영을 위한 자동화 시스템</p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Slack Alert 연동</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">배포/장애 알림 실시간 Slack 채널 연동</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Blue-Green 배포</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">무중단 배포 및 롤백 자동화</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">CloudWatch 모니터링</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">메트릭 수집, 대시보드 구성, 경보 설정</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Docker & ECR</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">컨테이너 이미지 빌드 및 레지스트리 관리</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- AI Development Automation -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border-2 border-indigo-200">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-800 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full mb-2">AI 자동화 특화</span>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">AI 개발 자동화</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Claude Code 기반 AI 페어 프로그래밍 워크플로우</p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Claude Code AI 페어 프로그래밍</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">AI와 함께하는 실시간 코드 작성 및 리뷰 자동화</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Git Worktree 병렬 브랜치 개발</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">여러 기능을 동시에 개발하는 병렬 워크플로우</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">tmux 멀티세션 터미널 최적화</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">멀티 세션 관리로 개발 생산성 극대화</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-violet-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">MCP (Model Context Protocol) 통합</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">AI 프로토콜 표준으로 도구 연동 자동화</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-violet-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">AI Design 연동 (Figma AI)</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">디자인-코드 변환 자동화 파이프라인</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-violet-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Openclaw 확장 자동화</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Claude Code 확장으로 반복 작업 완전 자동화</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Security & Monitoring -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">보안 & 인증</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">엔터프라이즈급 보안 시스템 구축</p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">OAuth 2.0 & JWT</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">안전한 사용자 인증 및 권한 관리</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">BCrypt & 암호화</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">비밀번호 해싱 및 데이터 암호화</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">API 보안</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Rate Limiting, CORS, HTTPS 강제</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">AWS IAM & VPC</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">클라우드 보안 네트워크 설계</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Technology Stack -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">기술 스택</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">검증된 최신 기술로 안정적인 시스템을 구축합니다</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-6">
          <!-- AI/Voice -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow text-center border-2 border-purple-200">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🎤</div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">STT/TTS</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Voice AI</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow text-center border-2 border-purple-200">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🤖</div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">LLM</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Language Model</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Programming Languages -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">☕</div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Java 25 LTS</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Latest LTS</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🐍</div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Python</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">AI/ML</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Frameworks -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🌱</div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Spring Boot</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">4.0.3</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">⚛️</div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">WebFlux</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Reactive</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Cloud & DevOps -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow text-center border-2 border-green-200">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🚀</div>
